efficiency cycle of material suction, grinding and discharge is formed, solving the problem of material agitation, avoiding circulation dead - ends, and achieving excellent grinding results in a short time. It is suitable for small - batch production (easy color change). Pre - dispersion and grinding can be completed in one lacquer slurry tank. The main shaft is speed - adjustable, with smooth operation, low noise, few auxiliary devices, convenient cleaning and easy replacement of grinding media.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.75em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(118, 146, 60); font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;适用范围/Scope of application&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;适用于涂料、油墨、农药、悬浮剂、造纸等行业物料的乳化、混合、分散，能使物料细度分布均匀，借助强力高速剪切功能，可在短时间内让产品达标。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;It is suitable for emulsification, mixing and dispersing of materials in industries like paints, inks, pesticides, suspending agents and papermaking. It ensures uniform fineness distribution of materials and enables products to meet requirements in a short time with the aid of powerful high - speed shearing function.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: var(--md-box-samantha-normal-text-color); text-wrap-mode: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: Inter, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;SF Pro SC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;SF Pro Display&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;SF Pro Icons&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;PingFang SC&amp;quot;, &amp;quot