stify-content: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;td valign=&quot;middle&quot; style=&quot;display: flex;align-self: center;&quot; align=&quot;center&quot;&gt;&lt;p id=&quot;_img_parent_tmp&quot; style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://lanmo-app.wsw88.cn/uploadfile/ueditor/image/202504/174355917492d66c.jpg&quot; title=&quot;FYFD电加热釜使用现场&quot; alt=&quot;FYFD电加热釜使用现场&quot; width=&quot;100%&quot; height=&quot;auto&quot; border=&quot;0&quot; vspace=&quot;0&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td valign=&quot;middle&quot; style=&quot;display: flex;align-self: center;&quot; align=&quot;center&quot;&gt;&lt;p id=&quot;_img_parent_tmp&quot; style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://lanmo-app.wsw88.cn/uploadfile/ueditor/image/202504/17435591813f0ad1.jpg&quot; title=&quot;FYFD电加热釜2&quot; alt=&quot;FYFD电加热釜2&quot; width=&quot;100%&quot; height=&quot;auto&quot; border=&quot;0&quot; vspace=&quot;0&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.75em;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;概述/Overview&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.75em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;具有加热迅速、耐高温、耐腐蚀、卫生、无污染、无需锅炉自动加温、使用方便等特点，以参加反应物质的充分混合为前提，对于加热、冷却、液体萃取以及气体吸收等物理变化过程，均需采用搅拌装置才能取得良好效果，还可为客户设计、加工外盘管反应釜。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.75em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-indent: 2em; font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;With rapid heating, high - temperature resistance, corrosion resistance, sanitation, no pollution, no need for boiler automatic heating, and easy to use. Taking the full mixing of reactants as a prerequisite, for physical processes such as heating, cooling, liquid extraction, and gas absorption, a mixing device is required to achieve good results. It can also design and process outer - coil reaction kettles for customers.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.75em;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;应用/Applications&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.75em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;广泛应用于石油、化工、橡胶、农药、染料、医药、食品，用于完成硫化、硝化、氢化、烷基化、聚合、缩合等工艺过程。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.75em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;Widely used in petroleum, chemical, rubber, pesticide, dye, medicine, food, for completing vulcanization, nitration, hydrogenation, alkylation, polymerization and condensation processes.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.75em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.75em;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;工艺特性/Properties of the Process&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.75em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;加热形式为电加热。夹套形式分为夹套型和外半管型，夹套油加热型都设有导流装置。搅拌形式一般有桨式、锚式、框式、螺条式、刮壁式等。高转速类有分散叶轮式、涡轮式、高剪切式、推进器式，供客户根据工艺选择。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.75em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;The heating mode is electric heating. The jacket types are divided into jacket - type and outer semi - tube type, and the jacket oil heating type is equipped with a flow - guiding device. The mixing forms generally include paddle type, anchor type, frame type, screw type, scraping - wall type, etc. High - speed types include dispersing impeller type, turbine type, high - shear type and propeller type for customers to choose according to the process.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em; line-height