ing: 10px 14px; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot; align=&quot;center&quot; width=&quot;90&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;11&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td valign=&quot;middle&quot; style=&quot;padding: 10px 14px; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot; align=&quot;center&quot; width=&quot;53&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;60 - 80&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td valign=&quot;middle&quot; style=&quot;padding: 10px 14px; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot; align=&quot;center&quot; width=&quot;80&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;3000&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;;font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 1.75em; text-indent: 0em;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;'),(11,1,2,'&lt;p id=&quot;_img_parent_tmp&quot; style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://lanmo-app.wsw88.cn/uploadfile/ueditor/image/202503/1742988194e59b86.jpeg&quot; title=&quot;SW卧式砂磨机1&quot; alt=&quot;SW卧式砂磨机1&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.75em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px; color: rgb(118, 146, 60);&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;工艺特性/Properties of the Process&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.75em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;该机设计先进，采用密闭式连续生产模式，产品研磨分散细度均匀、品质优良，生产效率高。物料在密闭状态下加工，有效防止干涸结皮与溶剂挥发。配备双端面机械密封，双重防护，实现零泄漏。全新动态分离结构，出料更为顺畅，易损部件少。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.75em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;配有外筒移动拆装支架，便于拆装与维修。送料泵选用齿轮泵或气动隔膜泵，送料量调节便捷，工作性能稳定可靠。此外，卧式砂磨机无需专用安装基础，可依据需求随时变更安装位置。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.75em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;The machine boasts an advanced design and adopts a closed - type continuous production mode. The product has a uniform fineness, excellent quality, and high production efficiency. Materials are processed in a closed - state condition, effectively preventing dry - crust formation and solvent volatilization. It is equipped with double - end mechanical seals, providing dual protection and achieving zero leakage. The new dynamic separation structure enables smoother discharge and reduces the number of vulnerable components.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.75em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;An outer - barrel movable disassembly and assembly bracket is provided, facilitating disassembly and maintenance. The feeding pump can be selected as a gear pump or a pneumatic diaphragm pump. The feeding volume can be adjusted conveniently, and the working performance is stable and reliable. Additionally, the horizontal sand mill does not require a dedicated installation foundation and can have its installation location changed as per requirements.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 0em;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(118, 146, 60);&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(118, 146, 60); font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;优势表现/Superiority performance&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(118, 146, 60);&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(118, 146, 60); font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;table&gt;&lt;tbody&gt;&lt;tr class=&quot;firstRow&quot; style=&quot; display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; &quot;&gt;&lt;td valign=&quot;top&quot; style=&quot;word-break: break-all; border-color: rgb(221, 221, 221);&quot;&gt;&lt;ul class=&quot; list-paddingleft-2&quot; style=&quot;list-style-type: disc;&quot;&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 1.75em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;粉末合金制成的间隙式动态分离器具有自洁性，无堵塞，超耐磨的特点。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 1.75em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;SW 系列卧式砂磨机选用由具有世界领先水平的 BORGMANN 公司制造的机械密封。其动、静环表面采用碳化硅，O 型号圈使用聚四氟乙烯，能承受腐蚀性较强的溶剂的侵蚀。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 1.75em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;为解决用户的特殊要求，SW 系列卧式砂磨机研磨桶体和分散盘有多种材料可供选择，如氧化锆、复合材料等，本机具有耐溶剂零污染、高耐磨的优良特性。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td valign=&quot;top&quot; style=&quot;word-break: break-all; border-color: rgb(221, 221, 221);&quot;&gt;&lt;ul class=&quot; list-paddingleft-2&quot; style=&quot;list-style-type: disc;&quot;&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 1.75em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;Dynamic gap is made of special alloy steel and it is self - cleaning, non - clogging, abrasion - resisting.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 1.75em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;Mechanical seal of SW is made of BORGMANN silicon carbide material; o - rings are made of ETFE and can resist corrosive solvent.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 1.75em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;To meet the user&amp;#39;s special requirements, the SW series horizontal sand mill offers options of several materials like zirconia and composite materials, which feature solvent resistance, zero pollution, and high abrasion resistance.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(118, 146, 60);&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(118, 146, 60); font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(118, 146, 60);&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;适用范围/Scope of application&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 1.75em; text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;适用于汽车漆、油墨、乳胶漆、炭黑、钛白粉、工业涂料等。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 1.75em; text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;It is suitable for automobile paint, ink, latex paint, carbon Iblack, titanium white&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px; text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;powder, industrial paint and so on.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 1.75em; text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px; text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 1.75em; text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px; color: rgb(118, 146, 60);&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px; text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;技术参数/Technical parameters&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;table cellspacing=&quot;0&quot; cellpadding=&quot;0&quot; align=&quot;center&quot;&gt;&lt;tbody&gt;&lt;tr class=&quot;firstRow&quot;&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;border: 1px solid windowtext; padding: 0px 7px; word-break: break-all;&quot;&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: auto; margin-bottom: auto; text-align: