gin-top: auto; margin-bottom: auto; text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;1950&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;border:solid windowtext 1px;border-top:none;padding:0 7px 0 7px&quot;&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: auto; margin-bottom: auto; text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;SW - 200&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;border-top:none;border-left:none;border-bottom:solid windowtext 1px;border-right:solid windowtext 1px;padding:0 7px 0 7px&quot;&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: auto; margin-bottom: auto; text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;200&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;border-top:none;border-left:none;border-bottom:solid windowtext 1px;border-right:solid windowtext 1px;padding:0 7px 0 7px&quot;&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: auto; margin-bottom: auto; text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;0.8 - 2.5&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;border-top:none;border-left:none;border-bottom:solid windowtext 1px;border-right:solid windowtext 1px;padding:0 7px 0 7px&quot;&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: auto; margin-bottom: auto; text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;75&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td style=&quot;border-top:none;border-left:none;border-bottom:solid windowtext 1px;border-right:solid windowtext 1px;padding:0 7px 0 7px&quot;&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: auto; margin-bottom: auto; text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;2240&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(118, 146, 60);&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;'),(12,1,3,'&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(118, 146, 60); font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;工艺特性/ Properties of the Process&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;环保型篮式砂磨机在封闭状态下运行，有效控制生产过程中溶剂的挥发，减少污染。其工作原理为：自吸叶轮高速吸料，研磨篮内进行极细研磨，分散盘高速旋转产生分散、混合、循环效应，由此形成吸料、研磨、出料的高效率循环，解决物料翻动难题，避免循环死角，短时间内可获得出色研磨效果。适用于小批量生产（换色容易） ，预分散和研磨可在一个漆浆罐内完成。主轴可调速，运转平稳，噪音小，附属设备少，清洗方便，更换研磨介质容易。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;The working principle of the environmentally - friendly basket - type sand mill: The self - suction impeller sucks materials at high speed, fine grinding occurs in the grinding basket, and the dispersion disc rotates at high speed to generate dispersion, mixing and circulation effects. Thus, a high - efficiency cycle of material suction, grinding and discharge is formed, solving the problem of material agitation, avoiding circulation dead - ends, and achieving excellent grinding results in a short time. It is suitable for small - batch production (easy color change). Pre - dispersion and grinding can be completed in one lacquer slurry tank. The main shaft is speed - adjustable, with smooth operation, low noise, few auxiliary devices, convenient cleaning and easy replacement of grinding media.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.75em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(118, 1