ot;&gt;此型式的分散器借助槽孔和多轮廓，促使研磨介质球体间产生强烈碰撞与摩擦，从而使物料得以高效研磨分散。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.75em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;The type of dispersing disk utilizes slot holes and multiple profiles to generate intense collisions and frictions among the media ball bodies, enabling the material to be ground and dispersed with high efficiency.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(118, 146, 60);&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(118, 146, 60);&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;应用/Applications&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.75em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(118, 146, 60);&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;适用于涂料、油墨、颜料、造纸、非矿填料等物料的超细微分散研磨，可改变筒体装珠量以满足各种不同物料的需求。具备强力冷却系统。采用微型研磨介质研磨，能达到高品质产品要求，研磨白料不会出现发灰现象。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.75em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;Applicable for super - fine dispersing in coating, ink, pigment, paper, non - mineral filler industry, etc. Can change the bead - loading quantity in the cylinder to meet the requirements of various materials. Equipped with a strong cooling system. Grinding with mini - sized grinding media can meet high - quality demands, and white materials will not turn gray.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 1.75em; text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 1.75em; text-indent: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(118, 146, 60); font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;特点/Features&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.75em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;粉末合金制成的间隙式动态分离器具有自洁性，无堵塞，超耐磨的特点。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.75em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;SWN 系列卧式砂磨机选用由具有世界领先水平的 BORGMANN 公司制造的机械密封。其动、静环表面采用碳化硅，O 型号圈使用聚四氟乙烯，能承受腐蚀性较强的溶剂的侵蚀。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.75em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;为解决用户的特殊要求，SWN 系列卧式砂磨机研磨桶体和分散盘有多种材料可供选择，如氧化锆、复合材料等，本机具有耐溶剂零污染、高耐磨的优良特性。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.75em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;Dynamic gap is made of special alloy steel and it is self - cleaning, non - clogging, abrasion - resistant.&lt;br&gt;Mechanical seal of SWN is made of BORGMANN silicon carbide material, o - rings are made of ETFE and can resist corrosivesolvent.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.75em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;In order to satisfy the users special requirements, the SWN series horizontal sand mill is optional for several materials, such as Zirconia, composite materials, which have lots of excellent characteristic such as resistant to solvent, zero pollution, highabrasion resistance.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.75em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-indent: 2em; line-height: 1.75em;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;color: rgb(118, 146, 60); font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;技术参数/Technical parameters&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;table cellspacing=&quot;0&quot; width=&quot;720&quot;&gt;&lt;tbody&gt;&lt;tr class=&quot;firstRow&quot;&gt;&lt;td valign=&quot;center&quot; style=&quot;padding: 10px 14px; border-width: 1px; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background: rgb(255, 255, 255); word-break: break-all; 